Dialog Module¶

The Dialog module contains the dialog boxes used to interact with the user in various situations. These dialog boxes allow the user to make settings, enter data, and manage different aspects of the application.

ActorsUCDialog Class¶

class Dialog.actors_useCases_dialog.ActorsUCDialog(action, option, data=None, parent=None)¶

Bases: QDialog, Ui_ActorsUCDialog

Class for managing the dialog that handles actors and use cases.

This class provides the interface and functionalities to manage the actors and use cases within the application. It includes fields for relevant data and emits signals when actions are performed.

Signal emitted when data is saved.

Parent widget.
